	<h1 class="title">为什么社交网络上的原创内容越来越少了？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/343708/small/343708.jpg?1449500883" alt="">
					</span>
